node.text:
“don’t worry i don’t get the hype either.”

The above quote was @charlidamelio’s TikTok bio during her rise to becoming the most followed person on the platform, at 122 million. 

Alongside sister @dixiedamelio, we have the D’Amelios: a seemingly normal pair of sisters from Connecticut who’re now TikTok royalty, living in the Hollywood Hills. How did this happen and how are they adapting to their newfound celebrity? 

Internet fame can be a lot to deal with, but the pair’s lucrative brand deals, upcoming Hulu series and slim work-life balance have put enough on their plates to keep them from overthinking their new reality too much.

#Linkinbio for the D’Amelios’ PAPER cover story.
